 EDITOR'S NOTE: <PERSON> Victoria </PERSON> <PERSON> Graham </PERSON> is <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> chief correspondent at the <ORGANIZATION> United </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Nations </ORGANIZATION>.
