<HEAD>Britain Celebrates New Princess With Flowers, Bets, 41-Gun Salutes</HEAD>
<NOTE>With LaserPhoto</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By EDITH M. LEDERER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
