deserve.'' Transportation Secretary <PERSON> Jim </PERSON> <PERSON> Burnley </PERSON> criticized the study. `` The highly partisan attack today by members of the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Task </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Force </ORGANIZATION> on Safety was full of inaccuracies and distortions,'' he said in a written response. He blamed congressional Democrats for not providing adequate budgets for the <ORGANIZATION> Coast </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Guard </ORGANIZATION> or the <ORGANIZATION> Federal </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Aviation </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Administration </ORGANIZATION>.
