<SECOND>AM-Britain-Stocks, 1st Ld-Writethru,0248</SECOND>
<HEAD>Stocks Fall</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: New thruout with closing figures, comment.</NOTE>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
